            <p>HBO's CEO has suggested that the TV adaptation of The Last of Us could be wrapped up as soon as next season.</p>
<p>Asked to confirm if The Last of Us' upcoming season was "final" in an interview with <a href="https://deadline.com/2026/01/hbo-casey-bloys-the-pitt-heated-rivalry-euphoria-interview-1236700801/">Deadline</a>, CEO and chairperson of HBO, Casey Bloys, said: "It certainly seems that way, but on decisions like that, we will defer to the showrunners. So you can ask them."</p>
